[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0128","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0128.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0467","title":"Webcom CGI Guestbook 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Webcom CGI Guestbook 的 wguest.exe 和 rguest.exe 组件存在任意文件读取漏洞。攻击者可通过向 \"template\" 参数传入恶意路径，利用目录遍历技术读取服务器上的任意文件，包括配置文件、密码文件等敏感信息。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，影响运行 Webcom Guestbook 0.1 版本的 Web 服务器，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议升级至最新版本或移除存在漏洞的 CGI 程序。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0467"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.433","remediation":"立即删除或禁用服务器上的 wguest.exe 和 rguest.exe 脚本，停止使用 Webcom CGI Guestbook 程序（已停止维护多年）。作为替代方案，部署其他仍在维护的留言本程序。同时配置 Web 服务器权限，限制 CGI 目录下脚本对任意文件的读取能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0467","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20446","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0467.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0467","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0467.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0467.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rrcj-vcw6-vg5f/GHSA-rrcj-vcw6-vg5f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0467.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3c4e87d4-fd7c-4a07-bd95-3b0615781d90.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0128.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0128.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0128.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0124","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0124.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0447","title":"HP MPE/iX Debug 工具本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP MPE/iX 操作系统中的调试工具存在权限管理缺陷，本地普通用户可通过使用该调试程序中的 debug 功能获取系统特权，从而实现对系统的完全控制。该漏洞影响 MPE/iX 系列操作系统版本，利用条件要求攻击者拥有本地用户访问权限，在多用户环境下可导致敏感信息泄露与系统完整性破坏。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0447"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.963","remediation":"安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBMP9904-006 提供的 MPE/iX 调试工具修补补丁。如无法立即打补丁，应从用户账户中移除 DEBUG 能力（capability），或删除非必要系统上的 DEBUG/PATCH 文件系统，限制仅管理员可访问调试工具，防止本地用户利用调试工具提升权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBMP9904-006"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0124.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0122","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0122.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0445","title":"Cisco IOS 12.0 NAT 输入访问列表过滤绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 12.0 版本运行 NAT（网络地址转换）功能时存在访问控制列表绕过漏洞。由于 NAT 处理数据包的顺序问题，部分本应被入站访问控制列表（ACL）过滤的恶意数据包可能绕过 ACL 检查直接进入内部网络，导致 ACL 安全策略失效。远程攻击者可利用此漏洞绕过访问控制，向受保护网络发送未授权流量。该漏洞影响运行 IOS 12.0 并启用 NAT 功能的 Cisco 路由器设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0445"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.720","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 12.0(7) 或更高版本，该版本修复了 NAT 环境下入站访问列表过滤绕过的问题。如无法立即升级，可在入站接口上配置 ip access-group 并启用 ip inspect 或 CBAC 作为临时缓解措施，同时避免在 NAT 接口上依赖纯入站 ACL 过滤。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1104"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0122.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0182","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0182.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0609","title":"SoftCart CGI 程序配置错误信息泄露漏洞","description":"SoftCart 电子商务软件的 CGI 程序 SoftCart.exe 存在配置错误，攻击者可通过直接访问该 CGI 程序获取未授权的私人信息。该漏洞源于管理员未正确配置 SoftCart 的访问控制或目录权限，导致敏感数据（如配置文件、交易记录等）可被远程用户直接下载查看。攻击者无需身份验证即可在受影响服务器上执行信息泄露操作，造成敏感数据外泄风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0609"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"检查 SoftCart 安装目录的访问权限配置，确保 SoftCart.exe 和相关配置文件不被直接通过 Web 服务器访问。升级到 SoftCart 官方发布的最新安全版本，删除或禁用不需要的 CGI 脚本，配置 Web 服务器的访问控制列表以限制对 cgi-bin 目录的访问，启用日志审计监控异常请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5a67adc3536b9edff12a57c2de9cd5aa5d12653d/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vmq4-9fwq-8hqr/GHSA-vmq4-9fwq-8hqr.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0182.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0182.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0180","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0180.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0608","title":"PDG Shopping Cart shopper.cgi 配置错误导致敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"PDG 购物车的 CGI 程序 shopper.cgi 由于配置不当，在特定请求下会把购物车系统中存储的私人订单信息、用户账户资料等机密数据返回给未授权访问者。该漏洞可通过网络远程触发，攻击无需认证，仅需向存在缺陷的 shopper.cgi 发送构造请求即可读取敏感内容，影响部署了错误配置 PDG Shopping Cart 的 Web 站点。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0608"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01","updated":"2026-07-17","remediation":"修正 shopper.cgi 的配置文件，禁用调试或信息展示选项，限制该 CGI 仅对授权会话返回数据，并在 Web 服务器层面（如 .htaccess 或访问控制列表）对 shopper.cgi 增加访问控制与输入校验，避免未授权用户读取敏感订单与账户信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3857"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0180.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0180.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1181","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1181.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1559","title":"Xylan OmniSwitch 登录提示绕过拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Xylan OmniSwitch 交换机在 3.2.6 版本之前存在一个安全漏洞，远程攻击者可以通过发送 CTRL-D（控制字符）绕过登录提示。该漏洞导致交换机仅支持一个会话，攻击者利用此漏洞可以锁定其他合法用户，使其无法访问交换机，从而造成拒绝服务。攻击条件简单，攻击者只需通过网络连接到目标交换机并发送特定的控制字符即可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1559"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-31","updated":"1999-03-31","remediation":"将 Xylan OmniSwitch 交换机固件升级至 3.2.6 或更高版本，以修复登录提示绕过漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T03:29:28.387824913+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1559","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92299263017061&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2064"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1181.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0106","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0106.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0434","title":"XFree86 xfs 符号链接攻击本地权限提升漏洞","description":"XFree86 的 xfs（X 字体服务器）命令存在符号链接攻击漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在临时目录中创建恶意符号链接，诱使 xfs 以提升的权限向受限目录写入文件，从而导致权限提升或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行 XFree86 的 NetBSD 及其他类 Unix 系统，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0434"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.283","remediation":"升级 XFree86 至 3.3.5 及以上版本以修复 xfs 符号链接漏洞，或应用 NetBSD 厂商发布的对应安全补丁。临时缓解措施：限制不可信用户的本地登录权限，确保 xfs 临时目录（如 /tmp/.X11-unix）具有正确权限（1777）且不可被符号链接攻击利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/359","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0434.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0434","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0434.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0434.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2g65-vp99-qwv8/GHSA-2g65-vp99-qwv8.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/359/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0434.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f067e6f3-94b3-4865-b51d-3ed58fe18b33.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1086","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1086.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1370","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 安装向导信息泄露漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 的安装向导程序 ie5setup.exe 在无人值守安装过程中会禁用系统屏幕保护程序，若安装过程出现故障或中断，拥有物理访问权限的本地用户可趁系统无人看管时直接操作目标主机；同时该程序会禁用任务计划程序服务，导致系统无法按时执行安全关键程序（如自动更新、病毒扫描等），降低系统整体安全性。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 5.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1370"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-23T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.730","remediation":"升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，在运行 ie5setup.exe 完成安装后，手动重新启用屏幕保护程序（控制面板→显示→屏幕保护程序）和任务计划程序服务（services.msc→Task Scheduler→启动类型设为自动并启动服务）。建议改用现代浏览器替代 IE。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92220197414799&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1086.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1906","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1906.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1397","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Index Server 远程注册表管理漏洞","description":"Microsoft Index Server 2.0 在 IIS 4.0 上存在信息泄露漏洞。Index Server 将索引目录的物理路径信息存储在注册表 ContentIndex\\Catalogs 子键下的 AllowedPaths 键值中，由于该注册表项的权限配置不当，本地及远程攻击者可通过访问注册表获取被索引目录的物理路径。攻击者利用此信息可进一步探测目标系统目录结构，为后续攻击提供情报支持。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 IIS 4.0 环境，CVSS v2.0 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1397"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-23","updated":"1999-03-23","remediation":"立即升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）及对应 IIS 版本，Index Server 2.0 和 IIS 4.0 均已停止支持，无法通过补丁修复。如无法升级，可手动收紧注册表键 `HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\ContentIndex\\Catalogs\\AllowedPaths` 的权限，移除 Everyone 和 Users 组的读取权限，并限制对该注册表路径的远程访问。同时建议禁用 Index Server 服务（cisvc）以彻底消除暴露面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1397.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1397","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1397.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1397.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vvqj-w228-7466/GHSA-vvqj-w228-7466.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1397.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000583.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8c819e08-07e7-43f1-8c2b-fa277db729fe.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1906.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0085","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0085.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0428","title":"OpenSSL SSL 会话重用与访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"OpenSSL 和 SSLeay 库存在会话重用漏洞，远程攻击者可利用已建立的 SSL 会话绕过访问控制机制，获取未授权访问权限。该漏洞源于 SSL/TLS 会话管理实现缺陷，攻击者在同一 SSL 会话中未经重新认证即可冒充合法用户，导致会话固定与身份欺骗攻击。影响早期版本的 OpenSSL 和 SSLeay 库，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。通过禁用 SSL 会话重用或更新至修复版本可缓解风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0428"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.500","remediation":"升级 OpenSSL 至 0.9.2b 及以上版本，该版本已修复 SSL 会话重用绕过访问控制的缺陷。当前所有维护中的 OpenSSL 版本（1.x、3.x 系列）均不受此问题影响。若仍使用已停止维护的 SSLeay 库，应迁移至 OpenSSL 最新稳定版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3936","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0428.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0428.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0428","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0428.json","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2020/openssl/gb_openssl_CVE-1999-0428.nasl","https://github.com/secure-software-engineering/achilles-benchmark-depscanners/blob/78b391f47cbe64adf7a2e2182ff94be604eb94dd/detection/CVE-1999-0428__org.jruby_openssl_0.9.4.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0428.md","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0428.yaml","https://github.com/SAP/fosstars-rating-core/blob/7b172f42f218f6cfad42f81bd9c9ef49de35b919/docs/oss/security/openssl/openssl.md","https://github.com/eclipse-ee4j/krazo/blob/a92003e894f263caa501df02fe1812b62ebbb8ee/dependency-check-suppressions.xml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0085.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0154","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0154.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0481","title":"OpenBSD poll 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 2.4 的 poll 系统调用存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制请求触发 poll 函数异常处理，导致系统内核崩溃或服务不可用。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 2.4 版本，CVSS v2 评分 5.0，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可远程触发，危害等级中等。建议升级到 OpenBSD 2.5 或更高版本以修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0481"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-22","updated":"1999-03-22","remediation":"立即升级至 OpenBSD 2.5 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 OpenBSD 2.4 errata 003 号补丁中修复。如无法升级，可下载并应用 OpenBSD 官方提供的 poll(2) 源码补丁（https://www.openbsd.org/errata24.html#poll），重新编译内核后重启系统。对于已停止维护的旧版本，建议迁移至受支持的 OpenBSD 最新稳定版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0154.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0155","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0155.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0482","title":"OpenBSD 2.4 内核 TSS 处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 2.4 内核的 TSS（任务状态段）处理逻辑存在缺陷，本地攻击者可通过运行 crashme 程序触发内核崩溃，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞源于内核在 TSS 切换时未正确处理异常状态，攻击者无需特殊权限即可利用，影响 OpenBSD 2.4 版本。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等，建议升级至更高版本修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0482"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:29.517","remediation":"立即升级到 OpenBSD 2.5 或更高版本；若无法升级，请从 OpenBSD 官方 errata 页面下载并应用 2.4 内核补丁 019（针对 crashme 程序导致的 TSS 处理崩溃），该补丁以 unified diff 格式提供，按补丁内说明重新编译内核后重启即可。作为临时缓解措施，可限制本地用户登录或禁用 crashme 等压力测试工具的运行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7557"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0155.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0098","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0098.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0433","title":"XFree86 X11R6 startx 命令符号链接攻击本地权限提升漏洞","description":"XFree86 的 startx 命令存在符号链接（symlink）漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在关键目录中创建符号链接文件，利用 startx 脚本以提升的权限写入或覆盖受限文件，从而可能实现本地权限提升或造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 X11R6 3.3.3 及之前版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0433"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.133","remediation":"升级 XFree86 至 4.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 startx 的符号链接竞争条件问题。如无法升级，建议使用 xinit 替代 startx 启动 X 会话，或确保 /tmp 目录以 nosuid、noexec 选项挂载，并启用 sticky bit（chmod +t /tmp）防止符号链接攻击。现代 Linux 发行版应迁移至 Xorg 替代 XFree86。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0433","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19257","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0433.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0433","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0433.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0433.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vfv2-37hx-mr4p/GHSA-vfv2-37hx-mr4p.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0433.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990331.data","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0098.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0098.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0078","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0078.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0425","title":"Netscape Communicator talkback 本地进程终止漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.5 浏览器的 \"talkback\" 崩溃报告功能存在本地权限滥用漏洞。当一位用户的 Netscape 程序崩溃时，talkback 组件未能正确隔离进程间操作权限，允许同一系统上的本地攻击者利用该机制向任意其他用户的进程发送终止信号，导致非授权进程被终止。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限且目标用户需运行易受攻击的 Netscape 版本，造成拒绝服务或关键服务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0425"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.143","remediation":"升级至 Netscape 4.6 及以上版本可修复此漏洞。对于无法升级的环境，建议禁用 talkback 功能：删除或重命名 Netscape 安装目录下的 talkback 可执行文件，或通过配置文件禁用 crash reporter 组件。鉴于 Netscape 浏览器已停止维护，强烈建议迁移至 Firefox 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0425","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0425.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0425","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0425.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0425.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7gf5-w5c8-cpr2/GHSA-7gf5-w5c8-cpr2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0425.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82494/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000580.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1533f373-1dea-4090-b2f5-07632a1ff6e8.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0078.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0076","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0076.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0424","title":"Netscape Communicator 任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.5 中集成的 talkback 崩溃报告组件存在任意文件写入漏洞。当目标用户的 Netscape 浏览器发生崩溃时，talkback 进程会以该用户权限执行文件写入操作，同一系统上的本地攻击者可利用此机制覆盖受害用户的任意文件，造成数据破坏或信息泄露。攻击依赖本地访问且需用户浏览器崩溃触发，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。建议升级软件或禁用 talkback 组件。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0424"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.030","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.51 及以上版本即可修复此漏洞；若无法升级，可删除或重命名 talkback 可执行文件（通常位于 Netscape 安装目录下的 `talkback` 文件）以禁用崩溃报告功能。作为临时缓解措施，确保 `/tmp` 目录设置粘滞位（chmod +t /tmp），防止非所有者删除或覆盖文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0424"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0076.toml"}]